
1] To create an object:

From the Setup page

Click on Object Manager

Click on Create >> Custom Object

Enter the Label name as Course

Enter Plural Label name as Courses

Enter Record Name as Course Name

Select Data Type Text

Select Allow Reports

Select Allow Search


2] To create an object:

1. From the Setup page

2. Click on Object Manager

3. Click on Create >> Custom Object

4. Enter the Label name as Student Enrollment

5. Enter Plural Label name as Student Enrollments

6. Enter Record Name as Student Enrollment ID

7. Select Data Type as Auto Number: SE - {0000}, Starting with 1

8. Select Allow Reports

9. Select Allow Search

10. Enable Track Field History · Click on Save

